But suddenly she made up her mind that her dress wasn't smart enough for a ball , though we thought it so lovely and so my aunt had to take her home . 
Oh , well said Archer with happy indifference . 
Nothing about his betrothed pleased him more than her resolute determination to carry to its utmost limit that ritual of ignoring the unpleasant in which they had both been brought up . 
In the course of the next day the first of the usual betrothal visits were exchanged . 
A visit to Mrs. Manson Mingott was always an amusing episode to the young man . 
The house in itself was already an historic document , though not , of course , as venerable as certain other old family houses in University Place and lower Fifth Avenue . 
It was her habit to sit in a window of her sitting room on the ground floor , as if watching calmly for life and fashion to flow northward to her solitary doors . 
She seemed in no hurry to have them come , for her patience was equalled by her confidence . 
