We had a frank talk almost the first . 
She thinks my impatience a bad sign . 
Merciful heavens a bad sign ? She thinks it means that I can't trust myself to go on caring for her . 
She thinks , in short , I want to marry her at once to get away from some one that I care for more . 
Madame Olenska examined this curiously . 
But if she thinks that why isn't she in a hurry too ? Because she's not like that she's so much nobler . 
