Do you ? He gave a reckless shrug . 
It's too late to do anything else . 
You say that because it's the easiest thing to say at this moment not because it's true . 
In reality it's too late to do anything but what we'd both decided on . 
Ah , I don't understand you ! She forced a pitiful smile that pinched her face instead of smoothing it . 
