Half an hour later , when Archer unlocked his own front door , he found a similar envelope on the hall table on top of his pile of notes and letters . 
Archer crumpled up the yellow sheet as if the gesture could annihilate the news it contained . 
A light was shining through the door of the little hall room which served Janey as a dressing room and boudoir , and her brother rapped impatiently on the panel . 
